{"tid":385652,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[Cult片式冷門動畫]18if","createTime":"2017-09-03T11:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T13:27:54.000Z","uid":34274,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ebd67a04b1255cb2aa20337662019e46c19d338e","tid":385652,"uid":34274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T11:34:58.000Z","msg":"因為第九話岩岩一次過追返，發覺套野癲得黎幾岩我胃口<br />\n<br />\n如果你平時鐘意睇cult片或者接受到Eva動畫最尾果種亂既話，可能都會好鐘意呢套咁特別既動畫<br />\n<br />\n不過如果你係好執著作畫既話就算喇，事關套野大部份既作畫都同劇情一樣咁癲，亂鳩咁黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一特色係每集既監督劇本作畫都係唔同班底，所以每集風格都可以好唔同，雖然犧牲左連貫性，但就每集都充滿驚喜，事關睇之前真係唔會估到佢會搞乜鳩，都係樂趣之一<br />\n<br />\n值得一提既係音樂做得好好，無論係BGM，OP定係每集都唔同既ED都有返咁上下質素，值得大力推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://myanimelist.cdn-dena.com/images/anime/7/86743.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyanimelist.cdn-dena.com%2Fimages%2Fanime%2F7%2F86743.jpg&h=aba3c500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ncopy and paste 介紹返:<br />\n  日本遊戲廠商 mobcast Inc. 旗下開發的手機遊戲《18 Dreamers》改編而成的電視動畫《18if（エイティーン・イフ）》，將於 2017 年 7 月 7 日起在日本撥出。<br />\n<br />\n　本作的故事背景起始於一種名為「睡美人綜合症」的狀況在社會蔓延，玩家需要深入不同的「夢世界」去了解並克服、打敗女角們諸如「貪吃、逃避、焦慮&hellip;」，等等現實生活中的心魔，最終讓她們化身成為女神幫助主角解救其他的女神。而由於舞台設定在夢境的關係，遊戲當中會出現一些熟悉但又異常陌生造型的角色，或者造型、畫風迥然不同的獵奇現象，可讓玩家一起發掘討論。<br />\n<br />\nOP<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3Oo7R_9WT_U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3Oo7R_9WT_U&d=wqF2iYvzm1E%2BmilzLiuNgjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e32bdeb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3Oo7R_9WT_U</a>"},{"pid":"39294e07c861bdd9562310733e44e85cd132c2cd","tid":385652,"uid":34274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"第三話ED「夢恋花」- 杉崎佳代（CV:田村奈央）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QdFc20tzHUQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQdFc20tzHUQ&d=wqF2iYvzm1E%2BmilzLiuNgjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=08246192\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QdFc20tzHUQ</a>"},{"pid":"f290b0f96f042db339227ebf12436f1baec423e4","tid":385652,"uid":34274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T13:45:31.000Z","msg":"第七話ED「too late」- ネネ（CV:水瀬いのり）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q5vcu-43j-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dq5vcu-43j-0&d=wqF2iYvzm1E%2BmilzLiuNgjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=fc3422b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q5vcu-43j-0</a>"},{"pid":"3ec784fd8c9d7d02dc1aa6ddd219e7edbe608e21","tid":385652,"uid":34274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T13:46:46.000Z","msg":"第九話ED「ツバサ」- 美咲（CV:新田恵海）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LJ5vEvapbX4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLJ5vEvapbX4&d=wqF2iYvzm1E%2BmilzLiuNgjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a9eba0fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LJ5vEvapbX4</a>"},{"pid":"88ce00dfcb2dbefb4961548b4ad0aabde7bde470","tid":385652,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad76712346a807f63bc782f3fcf4d2d98eba679","tid":385652,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:29:23.000Z","msg":"我覺得幾高汁... 集集ed同畫風都唔同<br />\n男主唔係正義撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25dfb8d4d449576670600b3cb14bf65602e226a9","tid":385652,"uid":34274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得幾高汁... 集集ed同畫風都唔同<br />\n男主唔係正義撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖